      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, meticulously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts a flawless original finish with a deep ceramic luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the seat heaters\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade machine.",
